#Alt+F1弹出功能菜单 Alt+F2弹出窗口菜单
Key F1 A M Menu FunMenu
Key F2 A M Menu WinMenu

#一些窗口操作的热键
Key F5 A 4 Close
Key F6 A 4 Maximize
Key F7 A 4 Iconify
Key F8 A 4 Move
Key F9 A 4 Resize
Key F10 A 4 FuncOnTop
Key F11 A 4 FuncFullScreen

#桌面切换热键
Key 1 A 4 GotoPage 0 0
Key 2 A 4 GotoPage 0 1
Key 3 A 4 GotoPage 1 0
Key 4 A 4 GotoPage 1 1
Key 1 A CS MoveToPage 0 0
Key 2 A CS MoveToPage 0 1
Key 3 A CS MoveToPage 1 0
Key 4 A CS MoveToPage 1 1
Key h A CS ResizeMove  50 97  0  0
Key j A CS ResizeMove 100 47  0 50
Key k A CS ResizeMove 100 47  0  0
Key l A CS ResizeMove  50 97 50  0
Key s A CS ResizeMove  50 47  0 50
Key d A CS ResizeMove  50 47  0  0
Key f A CS ResizeMove  50 47 50  0
Key g A CS ResizeMove  50 47 50 50
Key c A CS ResizeMove  50 47 25 25

#快捷键启动程序
Key x A 4 Exec exec xterm
Key t A 4 Exec exec xfce4-terminal
Key e A 4 Exec exec Thunar
Key l A 4 Exec exec leafpad
Key g A 4 Exec exec gimp
Key s A 4 Exec exec smplayer
Key o A 4 Exec exec xfce4-mixer
Key p A 4 Exec exec pavucontrol
Key m A 4 Exec exec claws-mail
Key c A 4 Exec exec gucharmap
Key b A 4 Exec exec VirtualBox
Key v A 4 Exec exec gvim
Key a A 4 Exec exec audacious
Key Up A 4 Exec exec audtool playback-play
Key Down A 4 Exec exec audtool playback-stop
Key Left A 4 Exec exec audtool playlist-reverse
Key Right A 4 Exec exec audtool playlist-advance
Key Insert A 4 Exec exec audtool mainwin-show on
Key Delete A 4 Exec exec audtool shutdown
Key f A 4 Exec exec ~/.mozilla/firefox-shm.sh
Key d A 4 All (CurrentPage) Iconify on
Key Print A A Exec exec $[FVWM_USERDIR]/screenshot.sh
Key h A 4 Functray
Key F13 A N QuickTerminal
Key r A 4 Module FvwmForm FvwmRun
Key F1 A 4 Module FvwmConsole
Key Tab A 4 WindowList CurrentAtEnd, SelectOnRelease Super_L
Key Tab A M WindowList (CurrentPage) CurrentAtEnd

Key XF86AudioMute A A Exec exec amixer set Master toggle
Key XF86AudioLowerVolume A A Exec exec amixer set Master 10%-
Key XF86AudioRaiseVolume A A Exec exec amixer set Master 10%+

Key 0 A 4 Exec exec amixer set Master toggle
Key 8 A 4 Exec exec amixer set Master 10%-
Key 9 A 4 Exec exec amixer set Master 10%+

#鼠标按钮绑定
Mouse 3 R A Menu FunMenu

Mouse 3 1 A Menu WinMenu
Mouse 1 3 A FuncOnTop
Mouse 1 2 A Close
Mouse 1 5 A FuncFullScreen
Mouse 1 4 A Maximize
Mouse 1 6 A Iconify

